## Comandos de Emergencia
```bash
# Reset completo del proyecto
rm -rf node_modules apps/*/node_modules
npm install
npm run dev

# Reset solo frontend
cd apps/frontend
rm -rf node_modules .vite dist
npm install
npm run dev
```
